prompts.frontCover:
Greeting card front cover, a vibrant and humorous comic book panel illustration featuring the people from the reference photo. The scene is a stylized, cute beach with impossibly turquoise water, whimsical palm trees, and soft golden sand. Lao Lao, transformed into a comic book character, is depicted as a superhero named "BOBA QUEEN." She strikes a dynamic, triumphant pose, holding up a giant, comically oversized boba tea cup like a trophy. She has a joyful, laughing expression. Jordan, also as a comic book character, is next to her, looking on with an adoring and slightly amazed expression, offering her a birthday cake with one candle. The entire scene is framed with classic comic book action lines and sound effect bubbles like "SLURP!" and "YUM!". The colors are bold, saturated, and pop-art inspired.

In the center of the image, integrated into the comic design, is the text "Happy Birthday to my SUPER girlfriend!" in a fun, handwritten cursive script that stands out against a stylized sunburst background. The overall style is flat 2D vector art with thick black outlines and halftone dot patterns for shading, capturing a nostalgic yet modern comic book feel.
prompts.backCover: A minimalist greeting card back cover in a vibrant comic book art style. A clean, off-white background with a small, stylized graphic of a single, simplified boba tea cup in the top center. The cup is drawn with thick black outlines and filled with bold turquoise and pop-art purple, with a few black tapioca pearl shapes at the bottom. The entire design uses flat 2D vector art. The bottom half of the card, especially the bottom-right corner, is left completely blank to accommodate a logo and QR code. The design covers about 20% of the panel, leaving ample negative space.
prompts.leftInterior: Greeting card left interior panel, full bleed background. A subtle, light golden-yellow background layered with a faint, oversized halftone dot pattern in a slightly darker yellow, mimicking comic book printing. Two stylized comic book sound effect bubbles burst dynamically from the top-left and bottom-right corners. The top-left bubble is turquoise with the word "ZING!" in bold, white, sans-serif letters. The bottom-right bubble is a vibrant pink with the word "POP!" in the same style. The design is energetic but not overpowering, using flat 2D vector art with thick black outlines, leaving the center clear.
prompts.rightInterior: Greeting card right interior panel designed to hold a handwritten message. The background is a solid, very light cream color. A simple, clean border frames the panel, composed of a thin black line. In the top-left corner, a small, stylized illustration of a birthday cake slice on a plate, rendered in the pop-art comic book style with bold outlines, vibrant pink frosting, and a single yellow candle with a small flame. In the bottom-right corner, a minimalist cluster of three small, colorful pop-art stars (turquoise, yellow, pink) adds a final decorative touch. The central area is intentionally left open and clean, providing ample space for writing.
